    for _ in 0..n {
        let a = read().parse::&lt;i32&gt;().unwrap();
        let b = read().parse::&lt;i32&gt;().unwrap();

        writeln!(out, &quot;{}&quot;, a+b).unwrap();
    }
}</textarea></div></div></div> <!-- body --></div></div><a id="comment-111487" class="comment-link"></a><div class = "col-md-12 comment"><div class="panel panel-default"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title"><a href="/user/jooshj">jooshj</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="#comment-111487" rel="tooltip" data-placement="top" title="2021-04-13 10:50:39" data-timestamp="1618278639" class="real-time-update show-date tooltip-click" data-method="from-now">5년 전</a><span class="like-box" >&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-thumbs-up"></span>&nbsp;<span class="like-count">1</span></span></h4></div> <!-- heading --><div class="panel-body"><div class="content-parent"><div class="content" style="line-height:30px;"><p>Python에서 input = sys.stdin.readline을 맨 처음에 작성한다는게 어떤 의미인가요?</p><p>아래와 같이 작성하면 에러나더라구요 ㅠㅠ</p></div><div class="source CodeMirror-readonly"><textarea class="form-control no-mathjax codemirror-textarea" data-mime="text/x-python" readonly>input = sys.stdin.readline

